JOURNAL ENTRY 7
I am Fzoul Chembryl, high lord of the Dark Shrine.  My precious mages , as you
call them, have allowed me to follow your minion.  Dexam, you overstep your
authority.  My mark is on these people, and the Imperceptor will know of my
