Because of the incursions along the River Tesh by Zhentrim forces, all allies
are ordered to gather in the caverns beneath the falls.  The dragons should be
able to hold back the beholders, but I expect Zhentrim troops to follow up the
attack.  As pay I pledge the standard portion when we loot Teshwave, Voonlar
and Zhentil Keep.  The plan is nearly complete; come at once.
Signed,
Lord Porphyrys Cadorna

JOURNAL ENTRY 41
The paper is heavily soiled, but you can make out, ...Knives untrustworthy,
cultists unreliable, wizard insane and T seems very dangerous.  Expect little
reliability from the New Alliance, especially over the bonded subject.  Will
need to set up our own observation team.  Per...


