Suddenly the roof vaporizes and King Azoun, his wizard Vangerdahast and a troop
of royal guards descend into the room.  One of the guards points at your party
and
says, Those are the ones who tried to kill you, your highness.
The princess leaps up and stands between you and her father.  They were under
