Both the Princess and King are in town in disguise.

Tavern Tale 2
A flame wreathed giant walks the Elven Court.  He only fears three ancient
artifacts.  One may lie below a waterfall to the north.

Tavern Tale 3
Many soldiers think the Pit is spooky.  Some have gone AWOL rather than be put
on guard duty there.

Tavern Tale 4
The city's sewer is among the more dangerous in the Dalelands.

Tavern Tale 5
Groups of red robed assassins have been patrolling the forest trails.

