The Princess always has some piece of purple clothing on, that's how to spot
her.

Tavern Tale 9
Someone has passed through recently with something he was sure would destroy
the plants.  He was waving a wand about.

Tavern Tale 10
There's a trap door in the altar which soldiers use to deposit all magic items
